- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of graph neural networks proposed by GoogleBrain and DeepMind. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of matrices in computation and investigation of networks.
